Joel Asoro (Sunderland) on #afc rumours: &quot;I've heard a little bit, but if I think about it too much, it becomes &lsquo;what if, what if.&rsquo;&quot;<br />
<br />
Joel Asoro: &quot;It came as a shock. It is clear clubs contact each other, but it's my agent in charge of it. I try to focus on my football.&quot;

Robert Pires on reported Arsenal target Thomas Lemar: &quot;I love him as a footballer, he&rsquo;s a brilliant player.&quot;<br />
<br />
Pires on Thomas Lemar: &quot;I think he can be the star player for France in the next five years, he&rsquo;s that talented.&quot;
